                            <comment id="12681695" author="kristwaa" created="Fri, 13 Mar 2009 13:05:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch 1a fixes the improper handling of the temporary database directory.&lt;br/&gt;
The directory will always be created as &amp;lt;database_directory&amp;gt;/tmp&lt;br/&gt;
Added two tests, one for database shutdown and one for engine shutdown.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m committing this patch ASAP, but feel free to still comment on it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12681707" author="kristwaa" created="Fri, 13 Mar 2009 13:24:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch 1b contains a few changes to the tests (make sure tests fail if exception on shutdown isn&apos;t thrown, and reload the engine code after engine shutdown).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12681708" author="kristwaa" created="Fri, 13 Mar 2009 13:25:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed patch 1b to trunk with revision 753239.&lt;br/&gt;
Keeping the issue open for a while to handle any problems and address comments.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12681712" author="knutanders" created="Fri, 13 Mar 2009 13:40:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, I don&apos;t see the NPE now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
